I burst into tears on a night much like this when Jacob said to me “Homer and Peter are generation one cabinland dogs”. It was the harsh reminder of how time ferociously paces on for everything I love. Years from now these cabins we made with our bare hands will be rotting into the ground, our ashes long ago scattered in the wind, with Homer and Peter buried in the yard next to the generations of pups we adopted after them. Until that inevitable time comes, we’ll be here, doing this, wishing it would never end ❤️ #love

“Sculptra BLL” done by @drpbellevue! I’m really pleased with the results so far. In my hips especially I’ve been noticing volume loss over the years that I just couldn’t seem to get back no matter how much protein eaten or gym sessions I do. I’ve had two treatments so far, the first I paid for, the second he gifted me. I think I’m going to stop here and give it time to work completely. For more info on what this procedure is and about Dr. Parikh checkout my video from last month ☺️🍑
